      "rationale": "The CFD solver is version-controlled and regression tests are maintained for core fluid modules. Documentation of audit trails is present for most simulation runs, though coverage of hemolysis sub-model tests is partial. Engineering judgement indicates the overall software quality posture is adequate for a Class III submission given the maturity of the underlying solver platform."
